Package: libetkxx-graphics-x11
Architecture: any
Section: libs
Depends: libetkxx (= ${Source-Version}) ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: The graphics addon for ETK++ implemented by X Window
 ETK++ is a toolkit most like the API of BeOS.
 Note: Run "export ETK_USE_XIM=1" when you really want XIM within X Window.

